{"tid":532172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［無圖］我個friend個老母真係好撚正","createTime":"2018-01-17T14:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T14:58:20.000Z","uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58bb940f92d98784ab2d7d77a3366180e326619f","tid":532172,"uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"個friend細我5年仲讀緊書，佢老母宜家先30中，睇樣完全唔似生過仔，平時佢地出街似足兩姐弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點係伯母離過婚之後就冇再結過，又好似冇再搵過新仔，有次上佢屋企食飯佢係咁撩我隻腳，食完飯之後仲拖我入房，跟住求其點左其他人落街之後同我嚟個大車，之後佢想除我褲但係比我拒絕左。自此之後我地見面都好尷尬，大家食飯嗰陣都唔敢望住對方隻眼，想問下各位巴打我朋友係咪基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c953375b461270ec9116e3318244fc85a99f6e7","tid":532172,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人作埋個完美結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b99319af11e29e4d13f37642b63e5458668d4d","tid":532172,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c953375b461270ec9116e3318244fc85a99f6e7","tid":532172,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人作埋個完美結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"由個post 沉"},{"pid":"64fc56ca487cbbb5a8ec98e976309f32a798a166","tid":532172,"uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d5b99319af11e29e4d13f37642b63e5458668d4d","tid":532172,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c953375b461270ec9116e3318244fc85a99f6e7","tid":532172,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人作埋個完美結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkg